<div style="text-align: left;">
<div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:300px;"><img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a2/Golden_Retriever_2.JPG/800px-Golden_Retriever_2.JPG" style="width:300px;" alt="800px-Golden_Retriever_2.JPG" class="image" />
<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:300px;">
<p>SCP-5118在被收容后。</p>
</div>
